{
  "stem": "9262.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Everybody wants to catch the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we were lucky if we could catch a potato, or a turnip, or a carrot, or a kohlrabi.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So if you had one or two of these things, you could go home and cook a little bit of soup, so everybody ate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So this went on for a little while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then we were looking, what could we sell?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There wasn't really very much we could sell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And somehow or the other, by getting the job and going to work, we got paid in coupons.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And on these coupons, we could go and get our weekly rations so we had something to eat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then, going into the Autumn of '42-- we are now in 1942-- we [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] were told not to report to work, that a general action was taking place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Everybody had to be in his abode, where he was living, in the block, and nobody was allowed out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the director of the block, who was responsible for all the tenants, had to have a list ready that when the Germans came, and they asked for the tenants of room number 1 to number 38, they got to be made available and to come down.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So the Germans did catch up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They came into our place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we had our identity cards from Germany, which was just like a passport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It had the German eagle with the swastika on it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they had our name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But it looked very official.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So when the Germans saw that, they just waved with their hands and that was the end story.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because they would read out your name, and you had your identification, and they thought-- because not many people had it.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
